Sales Forecasting Project

Overview
This project forecasts monthly global sales using historical sales and production data (Dec 2023 – Nov 2025). A power law trend model with log transformation and linear regression was used to capture demand patterns.

Objective
To improve forecasting accuracy for better decision-making in production, inventory, and supply chain planning.

Method
* Data cleaning and preparation
* Log transformation of sales data
* Power law trend modeling using linear regression
* Train-test evaluation
* Error measurement using MAPE

Results
* Forecast Accuracy: **MAPE = 2.48%**
* Strong alignment between actual and predicted values
* Reliable model for operational planning

Business Impact
* Reduced safety stock requirements
* Improved production planning accuracy
* Lower inventory holding costs
* Reduced stockouts and emergency shipping costs

Tools Used
Python, Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-learn, Matplotlib
